sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS (service-ca)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP<br/>TLS (optional)
    participant S3 as S3-compatible Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: External User Access via Gateway

    Client->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>Auth: OIDC/OAuth (platform auth)
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward to /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>URL rewrite strips /mlflow prefix<br/>Re-encrypted TLS (service-ca cert)
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>Check user permissions on<br/>mlflow.kubeflow.org/experiments
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Allowed/Denied
    alt Authorized
        MLflow-->>Gateway: 200 OK + JSON Response
    else Unauthorized
        MLflow-->>Gateway: 403 Forbidden
    end
    Gateway-->>Client: Response

    Note over MLflow,PG: Flow 2: Backend Store Access

    MLflow->>PG: SQL queries (experiments, runs, models)<br/>Auth: Connection string credentials<br/>TLS: PGSSLMODE=verify-full (when CA present)
    PG-->>MLflow: Query results

    Note over MLflow,S3: Flow 3: Artifact Storage Access

    MLflow->>S3: PUT/GET model artifacts<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials<br/>(envFrom secret or per-namespace<br/>mlflow-artifact-connection)
    S3-->>MLflow: Artifact data

    Note over MLflow,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Operator Reconciliation

    participant Operator as MLflow Operator<br/>8081/TCP (health)<br/>8443/TCP (metrics)

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch MLflow CRs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: MLflow CR event (create/update/delete)
    Operator->>Operator: Render Helm chart<br/>(embedded, in-process)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Server-Side Apply<br/>Deployment, Service, PVC,<br/>NetworkPolicy, RBAC, HTTPRoute,<br/>ConsoleLink, ServiceMonitor
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Applied successfully
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update MLflow CR status<br/>(conditions, URL)
